}}'''卡拉巴赫汗国'''（{{Lang-fa|خانات قره‌باغ}}，{{lang-az|Qarabağ xanlığı}}）是一个半独立的[[突厥語民族|突厥]][[汗國|汗国]]，位于今天的[[亚美尼亚|亚美尼亚]]和[[阿塞拜疆|阿塞拜疆]]，該國约成立於1748年<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.britannica.com/eb/article-129462/Azerbaijan |title=Encyclopædia Britannica Online: History of Azerbaijan |accessdate=2020-11-15 |archive-date=2008-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081118105319/http://www.britannica.com/eb/article-129462/Azerbaijan |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://vostlit.info/Texts/rus2/Bakihanov/frametext4.htm |title=Abbas-gulu Aga Bakikhanov. Golestan-i Iram |accessdate=2020-11-15 |archive-date=2017-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170711184500/http://www.vostlit.info/Texts/rus2/Bakihanov/frametext4.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，當時為伊朗的[[附屬國|附屬國]]。卡拉巴赫汗国的半獨立地位一直持續至1806年<ref name="gammer6">{{cite book |last=Gammer |first=Moshe |authorlink= |editor= |title=Muslim resistance to the tsar |origyear= |format= |accessdate= |edition= |series= |year=1992 |publisher=Routledge |location= |language= |isbn=0-7146-3431-X |oclc= |doi= |id= |pages=6 |chapter= |url= |quote=In 1805 the khans of Qarabagh, Shirvan and Sheki swore allegiance to Russia.}}</ref>，當時[[俄罗斯-波斯战争_(1804－1813年)|俄罗斯-波斯战争]]爆發，[[俄罗斯帝国|俄罗斯帝国]]从伊朗手中取得对卡拉巴赫汗国的控制权<ref>{{cite book |last=Swietochowski |first=Tadeusz |authorlink= Tadeusz Swietochowski|editor= |title=Russia and Azerbaijan: A Borderland in Transition |origyear= |format= |accessdate= |edition= |series= |year=1995 |publisher=Columbia University Press |location= |language= |isbn=0-231-07068-3 |oclc= |doi= |id=  |chapter= |url= |quote=The brief and successful Russian campaign of 1812 was concluded with the Treaty of Gulistan, which was signed on October 12 of the following year. The treaty provided for the incorporation into the Russian Empire of vast tracts of Iranian territory, including Daghestan, Georgia with the Sheragel province, Imeretia, Guria, Mingrelia, and Abkhazia, as well as the khanates of Karabagh, Ganja, Sheki, Shirvan, Derbent, Kuba, Baku, and Talysh,|page=5}}</ref>。1813年，[[沙皇|俄罗斯沙皇]][[亚历山大一世_(俄国)|亚历山大一世]]與[[卡扎尔王朝|卡扎尔王朝]]君主[[法特赫-阿里沙·卡扎爾|法特赫-阿里沙·卡扎爾]]簽訂《[[古利斯坦条约|古利斯坦条约]]》，伊朗正式將卡拉巴赫汗国割讓給俄羅斯<ref name="potier1">{{Cite book|last=Potier|first=Tim|title=Conflict in Nagorno-Karabakh, Abkhazia and South Ossetia: A Legal Appraisal|publisher=Martinus Nijhoff Publishers|year=2001|location=|pages=1: ''"Panah Ali-Khan founded the Karabakh Khanate in the mid 18th century. To defend it, in the 1750s, he built Panakhabad fortress (subsequently renamed Shusha, after a nearby village) which became the capital of the Khanate. It was not until 1805 that the Russian empire gained control over the Karabakh Khanate, from Persia."''|isbn=90-411-1477-7}}</ref> 。1822年，卡拉巴赫汗国被废除，成為俄羅斯領土上的一部分。

